data.description: VA assumable loan at 2.375! Stunning home in Gander Lake conveniently located near the community clubhouse & pool! Welcoming entry foyer opens up to the formal dining w/coffered ceilings & butler's pantry adding charm & function, and a dedicated home office/flex room. Open concept living opens to the grand kitchen which features an oversized island for 6, granite tops w/tile backsplash, pull-out shelving & stainless appliances. Laminate flooring throughout the common areas ensures seamless transition paired w/freshly painted interiors on most of the main floor creates an inviting atmosphere. A downstairs guest suite w/an adjacent full bath offers flexible living! Upstairs you'll find 3 beds, a spacious open loft & 2 full baths w/double vanities. The expanded laundry features a folding table & custom cabinetry for added convenience. Heavenly owner's suite includes an ensuite bath w/shower, garden tub & a massive wardrobe room, allowing you to adapt the space to your lifestyle. Step outside to your private fenced backyard, complete w/a covered porch & grilling patio, perfect for relaxation & outdoor gatherings. This home will certainly impress!
